{"tid":894443,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"（Web Game)召換推理高手 來場推理遊戲吧 (V2.0)","createTime":"2018-11-08T11:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T15:55:34.000Z","uid":180281,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dc70d22aa84fb34ec0c163197a056b0f5a46e588","tid":894443,"uid":180281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T11:53:29.000Z","msg":"總算改好哂啦, 可以玩得!<br />\n<br />\n一個結合狼人殺與推理元素的多人遊戲<br />\n網址: <a href=\"http://reasoning-game.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Freasoning-game.info&d=Hc1%2BdZ9%2BT6jd8PNkX1crppWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=59262b4b\" target=\"_blank\">http://reasoning-game.info</a><br />\n<br />\nV2.0 更新:<br />\n- 聊天室改用Socket 做Long connect, 唔會好似上次咁Lag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- 國王改由電腦控制(殺人次序請睇遊戲說明)<br />\n- 防走場, 3 次無操作者, 會被賜死<br />\n- 臥底可以知道其它臥底隊友係邊個, 請勿殺錯隊友(請自行按&quot;身份 與 行動&quot;查看)<br />\n- 如果有人無發問, 系統會隨機提供一條線索<br />\n- 計分/排行榜完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再次利申: <br />\n超新手寫Code, 太慢/有Bug請多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n注冊唔洗E-mail認證, 驚有私隱問題既請亂填<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/08/195126_9fae2ba51cb7e2060c740639aca8e872.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2F195126_9fae2ba51cb7e2060c740639aca8e872.png&h=c36687c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd83e2fcd2fb32a05d4e628980db37167e943bc7","tid":894443,"uid":180281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:13:23.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9eb9810acfd39abbe